{"tid":454401,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「上海仔」郭永鴻涉1億元洗黑錢案被捕","createTime":"2017-11-01T05:46:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T13:32:38.000Z","uid":51271,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"5d606d1056fd39e5ee7dd6159de4bfdbe8897469","tid":454401,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:46:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171101/s00001/1509514085464\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171101%2Fs00001%2F1509514085464&d=NvoLAQrF2iDzGXEcyQKP6gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=bd5f159c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171101%2Fs00001%2F1509514085464&h=b6ee7d25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171101/s00001/1509514085464</a><br />\n<br />\n警方毒品調查科財富調查組人員根據線報及經深入調查後，今晨約七時突擊搜查淺水灣道一單位，以涉嫌「處理已知道或相信為代表從可公訴罪行的得益的財產」（俗稱洗黑錢）拘捕一名59歲姓郭男子，並於該單位內檢獲小量文件。<br />\n<br />\n調查顯示，被捕男子涉嫌於2007年1月至2012年7月其間透過4個本地銀行戶口清洗黑錢，涉及金額超過一億港元。<br />\n<br />\n消息稱，被捕男子為黑幫「和勝和」前主事人（坐館）「上海仔」郭永鴻，他正被扣留於警察總部。警方指，行動仍在進行中，不排除有更多人被捕。"},{"pid":"11be6168f3e1355e488b3f041db410ca54ee2eb7","tid":454401,"uid":22858,"like":13,"dislike":6,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:46:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong><ins>細字濃縮試用版</ins><br />\n經crosscheck多個post，確信五毛名單臚列如下：三色貓、法國佬巫斯義、群龍共舞、優美開始、JR、RedBaron、Gladiclus、D_Wade、dewi、newlife、bbchu、十卜Ching、侵B、吾系甘開心牙、返六日唔撚易、毛澤東<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據一：五毛一見字眼空群而出</ins><br />\n連狗對五毛問題視而不見、置若罔聞，與全連登作對<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451623\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451623</a><br />\n【枕戈待旦】有關被連狗封鎖禁言之嚴正聲明<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/442843\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/442843</a><br />\n刺刀捅向習匪頭 鏟平地獄鬼國<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/439819\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/439819</a><br />\n【黑暗】濕鳩塞鷗兄已遭連尼住禁言七日<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/435231\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/435231</a><br />\n<br />\n<ins>證據二：五毛擾亂視聽妖言惑眾</ins><br />\nJR：(人手置頂) 屈毛黨名單<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/405731\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/405731</a><br />\nRedBaron：關愛座呢隻五毛都算高招<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451674\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451674</a><br />\nGladiclus：（大踢爆）關愛座hunter係5毛！被bam屈毛派親身指證！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451720\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451720</a><br />\nJR：要求admin立即ban左三位會員︰關愛座hunter, 濕鳩塞鷗, 1000歲人瑞<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/451747\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/451747</a><br />\nRedBaron（已改名）：香港獨立之後一定要實行獨裁<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/452801\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/452801</a></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b2ea112bc022af7430c9744c39e0a2dd9f48d198","tid":454401,"uid":39710,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:47:13.000Z","msg":"689呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4cf7f80afb74a810643a74ae9f36f2ff224a6e8","tid":454401,"uid":5026,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:47:44.000Z","msg":"佢之前同梁振英食飯喎"},{"pid":"920f0593fb7ad90b4b9b63b10b3094af877332de","tid":454401,"uid":47359,"like":11,"dislike":4,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T05:48:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">c</span><span style=\"color: green;\">o</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">n</span><s